File Structure

We'll organize the app into components and style files for better modularity.

src/
│
├── components/
│   ├── Gallery.js       # The main component to display the gallery
│   ├── ImageItem.js         # The modal/lightbox component
│   └── Modal.css        # CSS for the Modal component
│
├── App.js               # Main component that includes Gallery
├── App.css              # Global CSS (optional)
├── index.js             # Entry point of the React app
└── index.css            # Global styles (optional)
